      "content": "the problem is i don't think \"stepping away\" actually works. like, if i just take a break or quit the lab, the weight of everything is still there. the emptiness, the feeling that i've wasted my whole life... that doesn't just go away with a vacation. i'm just looking for a way to make the noise stop for good. i just want peace.",
